msgid "An error occurred while saving the rules."
msgstr "保存规则时发生错误。"

msgid "Custom Rule"
msgstr "自定义规则"

msgid "Select a custom rule file to override built-in rules."
msgstr "选择自定义规则文件以覆盖内置规则。"

msgid "Enable ACK Limit"
msgstr "ACK 限速"

msgid "Limit ACK packets to prevent bufferbloat. Recommended for asymmetric links."
msgstr "限制ACK数据包以防止缓冲区膨胀。建议用于非对称链路。"

msgid "Enable TCP Upgrade"
msgstr "TCP 升级"

msgid "Prioritize slow TCP connections (e.g., web browsing) to improve responsiveness."
msgstr "优先处理低速TCP连接（例如网页浏览），以提升响应速度。"

msgid "Enable UDP Limit"
msgstr "UDP 限速"

msgid "Rate limit UDP packets to prevent abuse. Packets exceeding the limit will be dropped or marked as bulk."
msgstr "限制UDP数据包的速率以防止滥用。超过限制的数据包将被丢弃或标记为批量。"

msgid "Enable Dynamic Classification"
msgstr "动态分类"

msgid "Automatically detect bulk clients and high-throughput services, and adjust their priority accordingly."
msgstr "自动检测批量客户端和高通量服务，并相应地调整其优先级。"

msgid "Optimized Algorithm Description:"
msgstr "优化算法说明："

msgid "Adaptive Control: Adjusts bandwidth based on latency; increases bandwidth when ping is below limit, decreases when above limit."
msgstr "自适应控制：根据延迟调整带宽；当 ping 低于限制时增加带宽，高于限制时减少带宽。"

msgid "Real-time Class Detection: Automatically detects real-time/MinRTT classes in TC and adjusts strategy accordingly."
msgstr "实时类检测：自动检测 TC 中的实时/MinRTT 类别，并相应调整策略。"

msgid "State Machine: Includes CHK, INIT, ACTIVE, REALTIME, IDLE states, automatically switching based on network conditions."
msgstr "状态机：包含 CHK、INIT、ACTIVE、REALTIME、IDLE 状态，根据网络条件自动切换。"

msgid "Filter: Uses exponential smoothing to filter ping times and bandwidth data, avoiding jitter."
msgstr "滤波：使用指数平滑法对 ping 时间和带宽数据进行滤波，避免抖动。"

msgid "Default parameters are optimized for most networks; no adjustment needed."
msgstr "默认参数针对大多数网络进行了优化，无需调整。"

msgid "Internal Parameters Description:"
msgstr "内部参数描述："

msgid "These parameters affect the internal behavior of the algorithm and usually do not need modification."
msgstr "这些参数影响算法的内部行为，通常无需修改。"

msgid "Modifying internal parameters requires restarting the qosacc service to take effect."
msgstr "修改内部参数需要重启 qosacc 服务才能生效。"

msgid "It is recommended for experienced users to adjust according to specific network environment."
msgstr "建议有经验的用户根据具体的网络环境进行调整。"

